'''飓风卡罗尔'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Carol}}）是有纪录以来对[[美国|美国]][[新英格兰|新英格兰]]地区构成影响最恶劣的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]之一，源于1954年8月25日[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]附近的一股[[东风波|东风波]]{{#tag:ref|[[东风波|东风波]]指的是沿[[信风|信风]]移动的[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="glo" />。|group="注"}}，然后在向西北方向移动的过程中缓慢增强。8月27日，系统风速一度达到每小时165公里，但又在转朝西北方向移动后减弱。一个强烈的[[低压槽|低压槽]]令飓风转向东北，卡罗尔随后增强成大型飓风{{#tag:ref|大型飓风指[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]达到每小时至少179公里的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]中可以达到三级或以上<ref name="glo">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2014-06-15 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml}}</ref>。|group="注"}}。气旋沿[[中大西洋各州|中大西洋各州]]和[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]沿岸平行移动，产生的狂风和汹涌海浪导致[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]、[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]、[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]、[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]和[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]出现轻度沿海洪灾，还有许多房屋受到轻度破坏。风暴加速向[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]前进，于8月31日以接近最高强度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]纽约[[长岛_(纽约)|长岛]]和[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]]。次日清晨，卡罗尔在[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]]上空转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。

狂风导致[[长岛|长岛]]近千套房屋受损，27.5万人失去供电，大量树木倒塌，还出现了严重的农作物损失。[[拉瓜地亚机场|拉瓜地亚机场]]和[[蒙托克公路|蒙托克公路]]被[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]淹没{{#tag:ref|[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]指平均潮汐高度和风暴产生潮汐高度之间的差距<ref name="glo" />。|group="注"}}，切断了长岛东部同外界的交通。新英格兰也受到卡罗尔产生的狂风和巨浪冲击，整个地区约有15万人家中[[停电|停电]]，电话服务也被切断。1545套房屋被毁，另有9720套受损。约3500辆汽车和3000艘船毁于一旦。新英格兰一共有65人丧生，1000人受伤。风暴还造成[[加拿大|加拿大]]两人遇难，损失数额约100万[[加拿大元|加拿大元]]。飓风卡罗尔一共造成72人死亡，经济损失总额达4.62亿美元（1954年[[美元|美元]]，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|462000000|1954}}}}美元），刷新了[[美国历史|美国历史]]上破坏最严重飓风的新纪录。其名称“卡罗尔”因此成为大西洋风暴命名名单上退役的第一个名称，以后永远都不会再在[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]命名时使用。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Carol 1954 track.png}}
8月25日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]东北部上空催生出热带低气压<Ref name="mwr" />。系统向西北偏北方向移动，于8月26日清晨增强成热带风暴并获命名为“卡罗尔”（{{lang|en|Carol}}）<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2013-052714.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2014-04-01 | accessdate = 2014-08-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812100736/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2013-052714.txt | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-12}}</ref>。气旋逐渐转向北上，并因外界环境总体有利而继续强化<ref name="mwr" />。8月26日，虽然系统这时尚属热带风暴，但[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]][[侦察机|侦察机]]的报告却表明其中存在一个直径约37公里的[[风眼|风眼]]<ref name="reanal">{{cite report | page = 71-72 | title = Reanalysis of Ten U.S. Landfalling Hurricanes | author = Chris Landsea | author2 = Mike Dickinson | author3 = Donna Strahan | year = 2006 | accessdate = 2014-09-19 | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/10_US_hurricanes.pdf | format = PDF | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140104102953/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/10_US_hurricanes.pdf | archivedate = 2014-01-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。次日，卡罗尔在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[卡纳维拉尔角|卡纳维拉尔角]]以东约545公里海域达到飓风强度<ref name="mwr">{{cite journal | author = Walter R. Davis | date = 1954-12 | volume = 82 | journal = Monthly Weather Review | pages = 370–373 | title = Hurricanes of 1954 | publisher = United States Weather Bureau | accessdate = 2014-09-19 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1954.pdf | location = Miami, Florida | format = PDF | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1954)082<0370:HO>2.0.CO;2 | issue = 12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110629054150/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1954.pdf | archive-date = 2011-06-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。由于[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]持续存在的大规模[[反气旋|反气旋]]影响<ref name="wc1954">{{cite journal | journal = Monthly Weather Review | pages = 228–236 | volume = 82 | author = Jay S. Winston | date = 1954-08 | title = The Weather and Circulation of August 1954 | publisher = United States Weather Bureau | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/082/mwr-082-08-0228.pdf | location = Washington, D. C. | format = PDF | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1954)082<0228:twacoa>2.0.co;2 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193319/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1954.pdf | deadurl = no}}</ref>，气旋转朝西北方向飘流。风暴继续强化<ref name="reanal" />，于8月28日达到风力时速165公里强度<ref name="HURDAT" />。系统这时的规模较小，其[[最大风速半径|最大风速半径]]也比其它同[[纬度|纬度]]和[[气压|气压]]的风暴要小<ref name="reanal" />。在最高强度保持了约30小时并移动了约120公里后，卡罗尔在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]近海略有减弱<ref name="mwr" />。

一个向东移动的深层[[低压槽|低压槽]]在行经美国东部期间得到强化，使风暴转向北上加速前进，之后又转朝[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]方向移动<ref name="wc1954" />。8月30日，卡罗尔在[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]以东约290公里洋面两次达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|二级飓风]]标准。次日清晨，气旋从北卡罗莱纳州[[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）近海擦身而过，侦察机估计其风速范围在每小时120到200公里之间。飓风继续以每小时63公里的速度迅速向东北偏东方向前进<ref name="mwr" />，并在进一步增强后以[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时185公里的最高强度从[[长岛_(纽约)|长岛]]东部登陆，已属三级飓风<ref name="HURDAT" />。快速穿越[[长岛海湾|长岛海湾]]后，风暴又以同等强度在[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]][[米德尔塞克斯县_(康涅狄格州)|米德尔塞克斯县]][[旧塞布鲁克_(康涅狄格州)|旧塞布鲁克]]（{{lang|en|Old Saybrook}}）进行了最后一次登陆<ref name="mwr" />。虽然移动速度很快，并且所处[[纬度|纬度]]也很高，但卡罗尔这时仍然保持着较小的规模和层次分明的风眼。气旋登陆时的强度数据源自[[新伦敦县_(康涅狄格州)|新伦敦县]][[格罗顿_(康涅狄格州)|格罗顿]]（{{lang|en|Groton}}）测得的[[气压|气压]]，为957[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.3[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）<ref name="reanal" />，当时风眼就位于该地区上空，因此这里一度云淡风轻，但随后而来的飓风强度狂风和[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]摧毁了整个地区90%的民宅<ref name="cobb">{{cite journal | author = Hugh Cobb | title = The Siege of New England | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_weatherwise_1989-10_42_5/page/262 | journal = Weatherwise | year = 1989 | volume = 42 | issue = 5 | pages = 262–266 | publisher = Taylor & Franics | location = Philadelphia, Pennsylvania | doi = 10.1080/00431672.1989.9929338}}</ref>。卡罗尔穿越康涅狄格州后又以飓风强度的最低标准经过[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]西部，并在这一过程中迅速失去热带天气系统特征，于8月31日晚在[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]]西南部上空转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。这场强烈的温带风暴继续北上，进入[[加拿大|加拿大]]境内后最终在[[魁北克|魁北克]]南部上空消散<ref name="mwr" /><ref name="HURDAT" />。

== 影响 ==

=== 中大西洋各州 ===
[[Image:Westerly,_Rhode_Island_after_Carol_storm_surge.jpg|right]]造成的破坏]]
北卡罗莱纳州从[[威尔明顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|威尔明顿]]到[[戴尔县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|戴尔县]][[曼蒂奥_(北卡罗莱纳州)|曼蒂奥]]（{{lang|en|Manteo}}）之间地区在卡罗尔来袭前收到了[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]。威尔明顿以北沿海地区的居民迅速撤离<ref name="theday">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Carol Whirls In Toward No. Carolina Coast | newspaper = The Day | date = 1954-08-30 | agency = Associated Press | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-QoiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=pXIFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2672,4855363&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | page = 1 | location = Wilmington, North Carolina | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190305001023/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-QoiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=pXIFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2672,4855363&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | archive-date = 2019-03-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。飓风途经该州期间产生的风力一直保持在系统东部，哈特拉斯角记录下时速145到160公里的狂风。更为内陆的地区中，威尔明顿和切里波因特（{{lang|en|Cherry Point}}）出现的阵风时速约为90公里<ref name="mwr" />。狂风导致玉米和大豆作物受损<ref name="ncdam" />，许多房屋及其屋顶也受到轻度破坏<ref name="ncdam" />，还有一些树木倒塌，多条供电线路中断<ref name="clima">{{cite book | author = James K. McGuire | title = The Storm of August 31, 1954 | pages = 289–292 | publisher = United States Weather Bureau | volume = 41 | location = Chattanooga, Tennessee | year = 1954 | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=0D7OAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA289&dq=hurricane+carol+1954#v=onepage&q=hurricane%20carol%201954&f=false | issue = 8}}</ref>。沿海地区有多个渔业码头因风暴受损<ref name="ncdam">{{cite report | author = James E. Hudgins | year = 2000 | title = Tropical cyclones affecting North Carolina since 1586: An Historical Perspective | publisher = Blacksburg, Virginia National Weather Service Office | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/er/hq/ssd/erps/tm/tm100.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131215201748/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/er/hq/ssd/erps/tm/tm100.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-12-15}}</ref>，[[克雷文县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|克雷文县]]的[[新伯尔尼_(北卡罗莱纳州)|新伯尔尼]]（{{lang|en|New Bern}}）出现洪灾。沿海公路也受到大浪的摧残<ref name="clima" />，该州一共遭受了约22.8万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|228000|1954}}}}美元）的损失<ref name="mwr" />。卡罗尔从[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]以东约160公里处经过，[[弗吉尼亚海滩|弗吉尼亚海滩]]的风速约为每小时65公里，[[诺福克_(弗吉尼亚州)|诺福克]]的降雨量达到100毫米。此外，风暴产生的降水缓解了[[哥伦比亚特区|哥伦比亚特区]]周边区域的旱情<ref name="virhis">{{cite report | author = David Roth & Hugh Cobb | year = 2000 | title = Virginia Hurricane History | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | archivedate = 2013-12-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131215202719/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/valate20hur.htm | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/roth/valate20hur.htm | location = College Park, Maryland}}</ref>。[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]出现小雨，该州和弗吉尼亚州所受破坏程度较轻，此外降水还延伸到了[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]境内<ref name="clima" />。

[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]有多条供电线路因狂风中断<ref name="prescott">{{cite news | title = New England Area Struck by Hurricane | agency = Associated Press | date = 1954-08-31 | newspaper = Prescott Evening Courier | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=e6FaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=k08DAAAAIBAJ&pg=5794,3272624&dq=hurricane+carol+new+jersey&hl=en | page = 1 | location = Boston, Massachusetts | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160428225336/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=e6FaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=k08DAAAAIBAJ&pg=5794,3272624&dq=hurricane+carol+new+jersey&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-04-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，导致两人丧生<ref name="spok">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | date = 1954-09-01 | title = Damage is High with Big Death Toll in Storm | newspaper = Spokane Daily Chronicle | page = 37 | location = Spokane, Washington | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6vlXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=mvYDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6151,207523&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503061841/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6vlXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=mvYDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6151,207523&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-05-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。沿海地区有多座浮桥因大浪受损，还出现了洪灾。邻近的宾夕法尼亚州有一辆拖拉机撞上火车，致使两人遇难<ref name="spok" />。新泽西州一共遭受了约25万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|250000|1954}}}}美元）的损失<ref name="clima" />。

卡罗尔在长岛东部登陆，登陆点附近记录下960毫巴（百帕，28英寸汞柱）的气压数值<ref name="nws">{{cite web | author = David R. Vallee and Michael R. Dion | year = 1997 | title = Hurricane Carol | publisher = Taunton, Massachusetts National Weather Service | url = http://www.erh.noaa.gov/box/hurricane/hurricaneCarol.shtml | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131215201648/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/box/hurricane/hurricaneCarol.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-12-15}}</ref>。岛上阵风时速达200公里<ref name="cdata1954">{{cite journal | editor = C. E. Rhodes | title = North Atlantic Hurricanes and Tropical Disturbances—1954 | journal = Climatological Data National Summary | year = 1954 | volume = 5 | issue = 3 | pages = 72–87 | publisher = United States Department of Commerce | location = Asheville, North Carolina}}</ref>，导致数千户家庭失去供电<ref name="redc">{{cite news | newspaper = Daytona Beach Morning Journal | agency = Associated Press | date = 1954-09-09 | title = 11,785 Families Hit by Hurricane | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=oFEgAAAAIBAJ&sjid=tcwEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4842,1444727&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | location = Washington, D.C. | page = 22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160514110021/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=oFEgAAAAIBAJ&sjid=tcwEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4842,1444727&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-05-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。大量树木被狂风刮倒<ref name="redc" />，多种水果作物受到沉重打击<ref name="clima" />。大量民房、船只和汽车受损<ref name="spok" />。岛上有约1000套房屋受毁<ref name="redc" />，27.5万人家中停电<ref name="clima" />。蒙托克公路位于[[苏福克县_(纽约州)|苏福克县]][[蒙托克_(纽约州)|蒙托克]]（{{lang|en|Montauk}}）境内路段被风暴潮淹没，长岛东部与外界的交通因此中断了一段时间<ref>{{cite book | author = Joan P. Porco | title = Holding Back the Tide | publisher = Harbor Electronic Publishing | location = Sag Harbor, New York | date = 2005-10 | page = 122 | isbn = 1-932916-05-9 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=5tTh9NNrv6gC&pg=PA122&dq=%22hurricane+carol%22+%22montauk+highway%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=4Yc_UZWnJ-ns0QGLpICwCA&ved=0CC0Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22hurricane%20carol%22%20%22montauk%20highway%22&f=false | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160425080707/https://books.google.com/books?id=5tTh9NNrv6gC&pg=PA122&dq=%22hurricane+carol%22+%22montauk+highway%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=4Yc_UZWnJ-ns0QGLpICwCA&ved=0CC0Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=%22hurricane%20carol%22%20%22montauk%20highway%22&f=false | archive-date = 2016-04-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[拉瓜地亚机场|拉瓜地亚机场]]也受到洪灾影响<ref name="spok" />。由于风暴规模很小，因此[[法尔岛|法尔岛]]（{{lang|en|Fire Island}}）以西区域基本上没有受到影响<ref>{{cite news | author = Maggie Astor | date = 2011-08-24 | title = Hurricane Irene Threatens New York: The Six Worst Hurricanes to Hit the Region | url = http://www.ibtimes.com/hurricane-irene-threatens-new-york-six-worst-hurricanes-hit-region-304394 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | agency = International Business Times | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140920152345/http://www.ibtimes.com/hurricane-irene-threatens-new-york-six-worst-hurricanes-hit-region-304394 | archive-date = 2014-09-20 }}</ref>。[[纽约|纽约]]有出现停电，但受到的破坏很小<ref name="milw">{{cite news | title = Death Toll Reaches 49 in Wake of Hurricane | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Milwaukee Journal | date = 1954-09-01 | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=uAQkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=ByQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4270,7452&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | location = Boston, Massachusetts | page = 1 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503072820/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=uAQkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=ByQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4270,7452&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-05-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。整个纽约州的损失数额约在500万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|5000000|1954}}}}美元）左右<ref name="clima" />，该州报告有一人死亡，数千人疏散<ref name="spok" />。

=== 新英格兰和加拿大 ===
[[File:Carol_in_Rhode_Island.jpg|right]]的埃奇伍德游艇俱乐部受到卡罗尔所产生[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]的强烈冲击]]
飓风卡罗尔在新英格兰地区产生的风速普遍有飓风或烈风强度<ref name="clima" />。康涅狄格州东部一直到[[鳕鱼角|鳕鱼角]]之间地区有近40%的[[苹果|苹果]]、[[玉米|玉米]]、桃子和[[番茄|番茄]]作物被狂风摧毁<ref name="nws" />，共计农作物损失约为2225万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|22250000|1954}}}}美元）<ref name="clima" />。新英格兰有成千上万的民房被毁，其中大部分是遭洪水或狂风摧毁<ref name="nws" />。一共有1万1785户家庭直接受到这场飓风的冲击，其中有9720套房屋受损，1545套被毁<ref name="redc" />。新英格兰还有超过15万人因狂风而失去电力供应<ref name="milw" />，并且实际人数可能达到该区域人口的三分之一<ref name="miami">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Leaves 49 Dead in East | agency = Associated Press | date = 1954-09-01 | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | newspaper = The Miami News | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=VjxYAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Zz0NAAAAIBAJ&pg=6239,91707&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | location = Boston, Massachusetts | page = 10}}</ref>，许多居民家中的电话服务也遭中断<ref name="clima" />。还有3500辆汽车和3000艘船被飓风摧毁<ref name="nws" />，风暴产生的暴雨也引发了多起交通事故，不过出现的洪灾程度很轻<ref name="clima" />。

整个美国一共因这场风暴遭受了4.61亿美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|461000000|1954}}}}美元）损失<ref>{{cite report | page = 8 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = Eric Blake, et al. | title = The Deadliest, Costliest, and Most Intense United States Tropical Cyclones from 1851 to 2004 (and Other Frequently Asked Hurricane Facts) | date = 2005-08 | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | archivedate = 2014-01-06 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/nwstechmemos/TechMemoTPC%234.pdf | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140106031407/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/nwstechmemos/TechMemoTPC%234.pdf | deadurl = no}}</ref>，其中新英格兰占了大部分<ref name="mwr" />，这一数额当时刷新了[[北大西洋热带气旋|大西洋飓风]]造成破坏程度的纪录<ref>{{cite news | author = Mac L. Hutchens | agency = St. Louis Globe-Democrat | newspaper = St. Petersburg Times | date = 1954-11-15 | title = Rash of Hurricanes May Bring Insurance rate Hike | accessdate = 2014-09-20 | location = St. Petersburg, Florida | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OhIkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=hXoDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2159,2872743&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160505143841/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OhIkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=hXoDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2159,2872743&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-05-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。同时气旋还导致新英格兰65人丧生<ref name="nws" />，约1000人受伤<ref name="clima" />。虽然损失数额很高，但与以类似强度袭击同一地区而导致488人遇难的[[1938年新英格兰飓风|1938年新英格兰飓风]]相比，死亡人数还是有明显降低，这主要归功于事先发布的警告<ref name="milw" />。不过，还是有一些地区因停电导致居民没有在风暴来袭前收到[[美国国家气象局|气象局]]发布的警告<ref name="miami" />。

康涅狄格州在受到飓风袭击前不久刚刚经历[[潮汐|涨潮]]，两者结合使得[[新伦敦_(康涅狄格州)|新伦敦]]以东的风暴潮有3到4.5米高，引发大范围潮汐洪灾<ref name="nws" />。[[纽哈芬市|纽哈芬市]]与罗德岛之间一条铁路被淹，导致约2000人受困<ref name="milw" />。新伦敦在风暴来袭期间的降雨量达到最高的150毫米<ref name="nws" />，狂风还吹飞了[[地方政府大楼|市政府大楼]]的部分屋顶<ref name="mcquaid">{{cite book | author = John McQuaid and Mark Schleifstein | title = Path of Destruction: The Devastation of New Orleans and the Coming Age of Superstorms | url = https://archive.org/details/pathofdestructio00john | year = 2006 | publisher = Little, Brown, and Company | location = New York, New York | page = [https://archive.org/details/pathofdestructio00john/page/54 54] | isbn = 978-0-316-01642-1}}</ref>。该州东部大部分地区因狂风导致停电<ref name="nws" />。狂风和风暴潮结合，摧毁了沿海地区数以千计的建筑物，其中有100套房屋被毁<ref name="redc" />。康涅狄格州东部还有大量民房被倒塌的树木砸伤<ref name="nws" />。该州在风暴来袭前有数千居民撤离，但还是有一人死亡<ref name="spok" />。由于风暴规模较小，康涅狄格州西部所受影响也很小<ref>{{cite book | author = D. G. Friedman | title = US hurricanes & windstorms: a technical briefing | publisher = DYP Insurance and Reinsurance Research Group | year = 1987 | page = 181 | isbn = 978-1-870255-70-7 | url = http://books.google.com/books?ei=AIk_Ue_zFMjB0gGWt4HgAw&id=0A0JAQAAMAAJ&dq=%22hurricane+carol%22+%22western+connecticut%22&q=%22western+connecticut%22#search_anchor | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160515000830/https://books.google.com/books?ei=AIk_Ue_zFMjB0gGWt4HgAw&id=0A0JAQAAMAAJ&dq=%22hurricane+carol%22+%22western+connecticut%22&q=%22western+connecticut%22#search_anchor | archive-date = 2016-05-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。该州遭受的破坏共计价值5000万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|50000000|1954}}}}美元）<ref name="clima" />。

[[布洛克岛|布洛克岛]]（{{lang|en|Block Island}}）上的阵风时速创下新纪录，达215公里，罗德岛州本土持续风速最高的是[[沃威克_(罗德岛州)|沃威克]]，为每小时145公里，阵风时速则有165公里。卡罗尔登陆时适逢涨潮，[[纳拉甘西特湾|纳拉甘西特湾]]的风暴潮高达4.4米，超过1938年英格兰飓风的纪录。[[普罗维登斯_(罗德岛州)|普罗维登斯]]因此被3.7米深的洪水淹没<ref name="nws" />。有新闻报道中称，该地区的洪水在一小时内就上涨到1.2米高<ref name="miami" />。市内有两座广播塔被狂风刮倒。[[华盛顿县_(罗德岛州)|华盛顿县]][[新英格兰镇|小镇]][[韦斯特利_(罗德岛州)|韦斯特利]]（{{lang|en|Westerly}}）也被洪水淹没<ref name="spok" />，冲走了镇上200套民宅<ref name="milw" />。[[纽波特_(罗德岛州)|纽波特]]也受到重创<ref name="spok" />，当地的[[纽波特赌场|纽波特赌场]]受损<ref name="milw" />。一些沿海社区几乎被完全摧毁<ref name="nws" />，全州有620套房屋和83幢其它类型建筑被毁<ref name="redc" />。狂风摧毁了数以百计建筑物的屋顶，迫使大量居民在风暴来袭期间疏散到避难所。数以千计的树木倒塌，大量供电线路中断，整个罗德岛州几乎全部出现[[停电|停电]]，95%的电话服务中断<ref name="daleo">{{cite book | author = Joseph S. D'Aleo and Pamela G. Grube | title = The Oryx Resource Guide to El Nino and La Nina | year = 2002 | publisher = Greenwood | location = Westport, Connecticut | pages = 58–59 | isbn = 978-1-57356-378-9}}</ref>。该州的经济损失约为2亿美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|200000000|1954}}}}美元）<ref name="clima" />，还有至少17人遇难<ref name="spok" />。

[[File:Hurricane_Carol_Storm_Surge_in_color_1954.jpg|right]]因飓风卡罗尔而出现的风暴潮]]

鳕鱼角有两万人在气旋来袭前撤离<ref name="spok" />。马萨诸塞州东部大部分地区的风力时速在130到180公里之间<ref name="nws" />。[[蓝山气象观测站|蓝山气象观测站]]记录下的阵风时速达到130公里<ref name="prescott" />，全州记录的最强阵风时速约为201公里<ref name="spok" />。狂风刮倒了约5000万[[板英尺|板英尺]]的树木，其中许多都倒在输电线缆上<ref name="clima" />，马萨诸塞州东部大部分地区在风暴来袭期间停电<ref name="nws" />，该州遭受的农作物损失约为1500万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|15000000|1954}}}}美元）。狂风摧毁了大部分玉米作物和近一半的桃类作物，该州损失的苹果有近150万[[蒲式耳|蒲式耳]]<ref name="milw" />。狂风摧毁了[[波士顿|波士顿]][[老北教堂|老北教堂]]的塔尖，[[美国独立战争|美国独立战争]]时期[[保罗·列维尔|保罗·列维尔]]用作预警的灯笼就挂在这里<ref name="prescott" />。不过原本的塔尖已遭[[1804年雪飓风|1804年雪飓风]]摧毁，这次被毁的是之后换上的塔尖<ref name="milw" />。波士顿各处都受到严重破坏<ref name="spok" />，[[普利茅斯县_(马萨诸塞州)|普利茅斯县]]的[[瓦尔汉_(马萨诸塞州)|瓦尔汉]]（{{lang|en|Wareham}}）有约1500人无家可归<ref name="miami" />。全州共有3350套民宅受到一定损失的破坏，另有800套被毁。飓风还摧毁了另外213套建筑物，另有530套严重受损<ref name="redc" />。沿海地区出现强烈的风暴潮<ref name="nws" />，[[新贝德福德_(马萨诸塞州)|新贝德福德]]的风暴潮高达6.1米，创下新的纪录<ref name="miami" />。马萨诸塞州有至少15人死亡<ref name="spok" />，损失数额约1.75亿美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|175000000|1954}}}}美元）<ref name="clima" />。

卡罗尔的强度在向内陆进发期间基本保持不变<ref name="carolmaine" />，新罕布什尔州境内的风力仍然足以刮倒许多树木并致使供电线路中断。有一人因树砸中自己所在的汽车导致伤重不治，全州一共有3人丧生<ref name="spok" />，经济损失约300万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|3000000|1954}}}}美元）<ref name="clima" />。邻近的[[佛蒙特州|佛蒙特州]]也有1人遇难<ref name="spok" />。[[缅因州|缅因州]][[奥古斯塔_(缅因州)|奥古斯塔]]的风力时速达到130公里，刮倒了数以百计的树木，其中一些又倒在房屋、汽车和输电线缆上，造成进一步破坏，有一幢建筑物被毁<ref name="carolmaine" />。倒塌的树木还导致公路封堵<ref name="spok" />，一人被掉落的树枝砸伤。多个[[县_(美国)|县]]失去电力供应和电话服务。[[安德罗斯科金县|安德罗斯科金县]]的[[利弗莫尔_(缅因州)|北利弗莫尔]]（{{lang|en|North Livermore}}）有数百英亩玉米被狂风夷平<ref name="carolmaine" />，该州的苹果作物也受到重创<ref name="milw" />，损失数额约170万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1700000|1954}}}}美元）。飓风行经缅因州期间降下暴雨，有地区在12小时内就记录下63毫米降雨量<ref name="carolmaine" />。海岸沿线有许多船只被大浪打伤<ref name="spok" />。缅因州共有3人遇难，至少8人受伤，经济损失约1000万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|10000000|1954}}}}美元），创下该州自然灾害破坏程度的新纪录<ref name="carolmaine">{{cite report | author = Wayne Cotterly | date = 2002-10-17 | title = Hurricane Carol (1954) | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131210224935/http://www.pivot.net/~cotterly/carol.htm | archivedate = 2013-12-10 | url = http://www.pivot.net/~cotterly/carol.htm }}</ref>。不过这一纪录只保持了10天就被[[飓风埃德娜|飓风埃德娜]]以1500万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|15000000|1954}}}}美元）超越<ref name="ednamaine">{{cite report | author = Wayne Cotterly | date = 2002-10-21 | title = Hurricane Edna (1954) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131210224556/http://www.pivot.net/~cotterly/edna.htm | accessdate = 2013-02-08 | url = http://www.pivot.net/~cotterly/edna.htm | archivedate = 2013-12-10 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

加拿大境内以[[魁北克|魁北克]]降雨量最高，达到108毫米。[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]][[雅茅斯_(新斯科舍)|雅茅斯]]（{{lang|en|Yarmouth}}）的阵风时速约为75公里<ref name="ec" />。卡罗尔的温带残留给魁北克带去强风，[[蒙特利尔|蒙特利尔]]的阵风时速有89公里，刮倒了许多树木，还致使多条输电线缆中断<ref name="mwr" />。[[新不伦瑞克|新不伦瑞克]]和魁北克都出现大范围停电，[[圣约翰_(新不伦瑞克)|圣约翰]]有三辆汽车被倒塌的树木砸中。风暴导致多架航班取消，蒙特利尔的地铁被洪水淹没。整个加拿大一共遭受了约100万[[加拿大元|加拿大元]]的损失{{#tag:ref|根据[[加拿大银行|加拿大银行]]的[[通货膨胀|通货膨胀]]计算工具，1954年的100万[[加拿大元|加拿大元]]相当于2014年的2095万加拿大元<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Bank of Canada | year = 2013 | title = Inflation Calculator | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | url = http://www.bankofcanada.ca/rates/related/inflation-calculator/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140921005344/http://www.bankofcanada.ca/rates/related/inflation-calculator/ | archive-date = 2014-09-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，相当于2014年的1910万8300美元<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Oanda Corporation | year = 2013 | title = 汇率牌价换算器 | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | url = http://www.oanda.com/lang/cns/currency/converter/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140924041723/http://www.oanda.com/lang/cns/currency/converter/ | archive-date = 2014-09-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>和1954年的约216.1万美元<ref>{{cite web | publisher = United States Department of Labor | author = Bureau of Labor Statistics | year = 2013 | title = CPI Inflation Calculator | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | url = http://www.bls.gov/data/inflation_calculator.htm | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190917111520/https://www.bls.gov/data/inflation_calculator.htm | archive-date = 2019-09-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="ec">{{cite report | publisher = Environment Canada | title = 1954-Carol | accessdate = 2012-12-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131211100301/http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=BBF632B3-1 | date = 2010-09-14 | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=BBF632B3-1 | location = Fredericton, New Brunswick | archivedate = 2013-12-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。该国共有两人遇难，其中[[魁北克市|魁北克市]]有一人因驳船沉没溺亡<ref name="spok" />。

== 余波 ==
罗德岛州因这场飓风遭受重创，[[州长|州长]]丹尼斯·罗伯茨（{{lang|en|Dennis J. Roberts}}）宣布全州[[戒严|戒严]]<ref name="spok" />。马萨诸塞州派出[[美国国民警卫队|国民警卫队]]到6个城镇防范抢劫<ref name="milw" />。国民警卫队员用飞机将[[干冰|干冰]]从[[纽华克_(新泽西州)|纽华克]]运往波士顿，对当地大面积停电情况下的制冷需求提供协助<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Ottawa Citizen | date = 1954-09-02 | title = Further Perils Feared | agency = Associated Press | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=LLM0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=HCsJAAAAIBAJ&pg=7227,356238&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | page = 23 | location = Boston, Massachusetts | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160428202058/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=LLM0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=HCsJAAAAIBAJ&pg=7227,356238&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-04-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。大片地区的停电持续了数天之久，还有些地方持续了一个星期，直到抢修人员修好中断的线路。停电致使制冷设备无法工作，由此导致的食品变质又造成了约100万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1000000|1954}}}}美元）损失。美国其他地区的供电企业前来提供协助。工作人员迅速清理了倒塌在公路上的树木。罗德岛州多家受损的工厂直到风暴过去三周后才安排雇员回厂上班<ref name="clima" />。波士顿老北教堂的尖顶于1955年重建，全国各地为此一共捐献了15万美元<ref>{{cite news | agency = International News Service | date = 1955-05-26 | newspaper = The News-Sentinel | title = Third Steeple Going Up on Boston Church | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Q9FUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=GTwNAAAAIBAJ&pg=4311,5339860&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | location = Boston, Massachusetts | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160425082427/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Q9FUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=GTwNAAAAIBAJ&pg=4311,5339860&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-04-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[缅因州州长|缅因州州长]]伯顿·克罗斯（{{lang|en|Burton M. Cross}}）宣传该州进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]。美国小企业管理局宣布缅因州6个县成为灾区<ref name="carolmaine" />。风暴过后的几天里，[[美国总统|美国总统]][[德怀特·艾森豪威尔|德怀特·艾森豪威尔]]宣布马萨诸塞州和罗德岛州为联邦灾区，[[美国联邦政府|联邦政府]]向马萨诸塞州提供了150万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1500000|1954}}}}美元）财政援助<ref name="mi94">{{cite news | newspaper = The Miami News | date = 1954-09-04 | agency = Associated Press | title = New Storms Slow Hurricane Repairs | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=WTxYAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Zz0NAAAAIBAJ&pg=4895,1289692&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | location = Boston, Massachusetts | page = 1}}</ref>，总统还下令军队协助善后工作。[[美国红十字会|美国]][[红十字会|红十字会]]迅速派出工作组前往受灾最严重的地区<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Spokane Daily Chronicle | date = 1954-09-01 | title = Aid Ordered for Storm Area | agency = Associated Press | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6vlXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=mvYDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20carol&pg=6539%2C209363 | location = Fraser, Colorado | page = 37 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160430081857/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6vlXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=mvYDAAAAIBAJ&dq=hurricane%20carol&pg=6539,209363 | archive-date = 2016-04-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，为数以百计的家庭提供食品<ref name="milw" />。卡罗尔袭击新英格兰约12天后，飓风埃德娜又吹袭了马萨诸塞州东部，造成20人死亡，损失数额达4000万美元（1954年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|40000000|1954}}}}美元）<ref name="mwr" />，为此该地区又获得了更多的救灾援助<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Spokane Daily Chronicle | date = 1954-09-16 | title = East Disaster Help Widened | agency = United Press | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=9_lXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=mvYDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6242,4152800&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | location = Columbus, Ohio | page = 48 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160427212422/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=9_lXAAAAIBAJ&sjid=mvYDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6242,4152800&dq=hurricane+carol&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-04-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

1954年有包括飓风卡罗尔、埃德娜和[[飓风黑兹尔|黑兹尔]]在内的多场飓风造成严重破坏，美国政府为此投入研究，建立国家飓风研究项目。[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]和飓风猎人侦察机会对之后的飓风进行研究，搜集数据来判断其结构，政府还进行了[[破风计划|破风计划]]，试图利用[[碘化银|碘化银]]来减弱风暴强度。<ref>{{cite news | author = Ray Bruner | date = 1963-09-18 | title = Hurricane Fighters Seek Achilles' Heel in Storm | newspaper = Toledo Blade | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=RrFOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=PQEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7206,1611569&dq=hurricane+carol+1954&hl=en | page = 5 | location = Toledo, Ohio | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160502051106/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=RrFOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=PQEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7206,1611569&dq=hurricane+carol+1954&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-05-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

由于这场风暴造成了惨重的人员伤亡和财产损失，其名称“卡罗尔”（{{lang|en|Carol}}）因此在之后10年都没有再度使用。这一名称在1965年重新启用，但随后就予以退役，再也没有用来给[[北大西洋热带气旋|大西洋飓风]]命名。<ref>{{cite report | author = Gary Padgett, Jack Beven, James Lewis Free, Sandy Delgado | date = 2012-05-23 | title = Subject: B3) What storm names have been retired? | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | accessdate = 2014-09-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111163143/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/B3.html | archivedate = 2013-11-11 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/B3.html | location = Miami, Florida | deadurl = no}}</ref>

